      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold uppercase text-white mb-4 tracking-wide">RETURN FAQ</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">Common questions about returns and exchanges</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">How long do I have to return an item?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">You have 30 days from the delivery date to return items. Holiday purchases made between November 1st and December 31st can be returned until January 31st.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Do I have to pay for return shipping?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">No, we provide prepaid return shipping labels for all returns within the United States. International customers are responsible for return shipping costs.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Can I return items purchased with a discount code?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Yes, items purchased with discount codes can be returned. The refund amount will be the actual amount paid after the discount was applied.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">What if I lost my receipt or order confirmation?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">No problem! We can look up your order using your email address or phone number. You can also log into your account to view your order history.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Can I return a gift?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Yes, gifts can be returned with a gift receipt for store credit or exchanged for a different size/color. Without a gift receipt, we can offer store credit for the current selling price.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">How long does it take to process a refund?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Once we receive your return, it takes 2-3 business days to process. Refunds to your original payment method take an additional 5-7 business days to appear.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

